{"id": "1338485435042889738", "channel_id": "1180850818509971466", "type": 0, "author_id": "655338276554801152", "author_name": "arr5721", "author_bot": false, "content": "除非抓好羊媽回血，不然沒復活的情況下傷痛有點難控吧\n但這情況下開局抓堅韌也不太會是優先的，除非有後手增益卡(反正我的玩法是這樣", "timestamp": "2025-02-10T12:23:15.571000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
